events.name: Portland Trail Blazers at Houston Rockets

headlines.description: — Victor Oladipo scored 25 points and the Houston Rockets shook off a terrible first quarter and held on late to beat the Portland Trail Blazers 104-101 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Oladipo has 25 points, Rockets beat Trail Blazers 104-101

events.name: Los Angeles Lakers at Detroit Pistons

headlines.description: — Blake Griffin scored 23 points and the Detroit Pistons took advantage of Anthony Davis' absence Thursday night in a 107-92 victory over the Los Angeles Lakers.
headlines.shortLinkText: With Davis out, Lakers fall to Pistons 107-92

headlines.description: — Actual ticketholders were back at a Miami Heat game for the first time since March. The Los Angeles Clippers had many of them deciding to leave early.
headlines.shortLinkText: Clippers rally from 18 points down, top ailing Heat 109-105

events.name: Golden State Warriors at Phoenix Suns

headlines.description: — Mikal Bridges scored 20 points, Deandre Ayton added 12 points and 13 rebounds and the Phoenix Suns pulled away in the second half to beat the Golden State Warriors 114-93 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Suns snap 3-game skid, roll to 114-93 win over Warriors
